<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5248861>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–7. Picobia dziabaszewskii sp. nov. Female. 1—dorsal view. 2—ventral view, 3—hypostomal apex, 4—peritremes, 5—propodonotal setae vi, 6—terminal opisthosoma in ventral view, 7—claws of leg III. Scale bars: 1, 2 =100 µm; 3, 4, 5,7 = 25 µm; 6 = 50µm." ;
